  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Create bullying-free spaces in 2 Mexican schools</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fundacion en Movimiento works to eradicate bullying through the promotion of the Culture of Peace. It seeks to benefit 2 low-income schools in Mexico that suffer a high degree of bullying, fostering an environment of healthy coexistence, through strategies that promote respect, empathy and generosity. It will raise awareness among the entire school community of the importance that children studying feeling safe, heard and respected. The work includes students, teachers and parents.</narrative>
  </description>
